The '''[[Defel/Legends|Defel]] Mimicker''' was an advanced [[Stealth field generator/Legends|stealth field generator]] used in the period following the [[Jedi Civil War]]. Designed to mimic the appearance of Defels as vague shadows, it was not disrupted as easily as other stealth units.

==Appearances==
*''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''

